	<b>Louis Mamakos</b> is Chief Technology Office at <a href="http://www.vonage.com">Vonage</a>.  He oversees all technology functions at Vonage, which includes new product and services development, supervision of all research projects and integration of all technology-based activities into Vonage's corporate strategy.  Mr. Mamakos has more than 20 years of experience in Internet technical engineering and architecture for large scale, commercial IP backbone networks. In the past Mr. Mamakos has held various positions at Hyperchip, UUNET Technologies, and MCI. For more information on Vonage see <a href="http://www.vonage.com">Vonage</a>	
